{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_2","type":"command_execution","command":"\"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\PowerShell\\\\7\\\\pwsh.exe\" -Command \"Get-Content -Raw 'C:\\\\Users\\\\jairo\\\\.agents\\\\skills\\\\react-best-practices\\\\SKILL.md'; Get-ChildItem -Force; rg --files -g 'AGENTS.md' -g '\"'!node_modules'\"' -g '\"'!dist'\"'; rg -n \\\"TASK-021|Card|Surface|Badge|Chip\\\" docs/frontend-tasks-v2.md docs/frontend-specification-v2.md docs/frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md\"","aggregated_output":"\r\n    Directory: E:\\CodeRepo\\shop-api\r\n\r\n\u001b[32;1mMode   \u001b[0m\u001b[32;1m              LastWriteTime\u001b[0m \u001b[32;1;3m        Length\u001b[0m\u001b[32;1m Name\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32;1m----   \u001b[0m \u001b[32;1m             -------------\u001b[0m \u001b[32;1m        ------\u001b[0m \u001b[32;1m----\u001b[0m\r\nd----          30/06/2026    13:37                \u001b[44;1m.agents\u001b[0m\r\nd----          13/07/2026    20:59                \u001b[44;1m.codex-runs\u001b[0m\r\nd--h-          13/07/2026    20:59                \u001b[44;1m.git\u001b[0m\r\nd----          02/07/2026    20:12                \u001b[44;1maspnet-api\u001b[0m\r\nd----          13/07/2026    20:59                \u001b[44;1mdocs\u001b[0m\r\nd----          13/07/2026    19:43                \u001b[44;1mfrontend\u001b[0m\r\n-a---          13/07/2026    15:38            345 .editorconfig\r\n-a---          13/07/2026    18:46           1988 .gitignore\r\n-a---          13/07/2026    17:22           2319 AGENTS.md\r\n-a---          08/07/2026    12:13       23454729 \u001b[31;1mfrontend.7z\u001b[0m\r\n-a---          08/07/2026    22:18          42350 openapi.yaml\r\n-a---          02/07/2026    20:12           3198 README.md\r\n-a---          13/07/2026    18:19          19265 run-codex-batch.py\r\nAGENTS.md\ndocs/frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:152:- `Card`, `Surface`, `Badge`, `Chip`.\r\ndocs/frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:208:- Cards, grid, paginação, vazios e erro